144
00:11:54.595 --> 00:11:57.724
And now... Iet's crack this egg.

145
00:12:18.372 --> 00:12:20.249
Excellent.

146
00:12:24.003 --> 00:12:25.254
Yuck!

147
00:12:30.886 --> 00:12:35.266
What?! You spent 2.000 years
looking for a tub of snot?!

148
00:12:35.892 --> 00:12:38.393
Patience. motor-mouth. Watch.

149
00:12:42.147 --> 00:12:44.024
