154
00:13:12.180 --> 00:13:15.310
The Ooze is back!

155
00:13:15.310 --> 00:13:16.560
Yeah!

156
00:13:16.560 --> 00:13:19.689
- He's so handsome!
- Why. thank you.

157
00:13:19.689 --> 00:13:24.067
I am Lord Zedd. sworn enemy
of all that is good and decent.

158
00:13:24.067 --> 00:13:29.073
