- How can I ever repay you?

159
00:13:29.698 --> 00:13:33.453
Do you recall the name Zordon of Eltar?

160
00:13:42.213 --> 00:13:44.715
I think he's heard of him.

161
00:13:49.096 --> 00:13:54.727
I want you to destroy Zordon... so that
my evil may once again reign supreme!

162
00:13:54.727 --> 00:13:57.854
I will not only destroy him...

163
00:13:57.854 --> 00:14:00.983
I will obliterate his entire legacy.

164
00:14:00.983 --> 00:14:04.738
It will be as if Zordon of Eltar never existed!

165
00:14:04.738 --> 00:14:07.866
- Finally. a real man!
- ( growls )

166
00:14:09.743 --> 00:14:12.870
