( squelching )

248
00:19:55.909 --> 00:19:57.785
Well. almost nobody.

249
00:20:14.679 --> 00:20:17.181
Hey. pretty fancy-schmancy.

250
00:20:17.808 --> 00:20:20.934
I guess if you invest
your money well over 60 centuries.

251
00:20:20.934 --> 00:20:23.438
you can buy something pretty nice.

252
00:20:24.689 --> 00:20:25.941
Uh-oh.

253
00:20:25.941 --> 00:20:27.818
( laughs )

254
00:20:28.443 --> 00:20:31.572
Aye-yai-yai-yai-yai-yai-yai....

255
00:20:31.572 --> 00:20:37.203
You haven't changed. Ooze. You're still
picking on creatures smaller than yourself.

256
00:20:37.203 --> 00:20:43.458
Put a sock in it. Z! 10 minutes out of the egg
and I'm listening to one of your lectures.

257
00:20:43.458 --> 00:20:46.588
You locked me into your
stuffy hyperlock chamber

258
00:20:46.588 --> 00:20:50.343
and tossed me away in the depths
like yesterday's trash.

259
00:20:50.343 --> 00:20:56.599
You any idea what it's like to be locked up
in a rotten egg for 6.000 years? It's boring.

260
00:20:56.599 --> 00:20:59.728
Not to mention I've had a charley horse
since the Renaissance.

261
00:21:00.352 --> 00:21:05.358
- You won't get away with this. Ooze.
- You robbed me of my prime.

262
00:21:05.358 --> 00:21:10.364
I was the supreme ruler
of the most foul empire in the universe.

263
00:21:10.364 --> 00:21:14.118
And now... it's time to pay the piper.

264
00:21:19.124 --> 00:21:21.626
Oh. the things that I have missed!

265
00:21:21.626 --> 00:21:23.504
The Black Plague!

266
00:21:24.755 --> 00:21:27.257
The Spanish lnquisition!

267
00:21:31.011 --> 00:21:33.514
The Brady Bunch reunion!

268
00:21:34.766 --> 00:21:36.643
( laughs )

269
00:22:00.418 --> 00:22:04.173
- BILLY: This place gives me the creeps.
- AISHA: I heard that.

270
00:22:10.429 --> 00:22:13.557
TOMMY: I've got a bad feelin'
about this place.

271
00:22:21.066 --> 00:22:22.317
( squawking )

272
00:22:23.568 --> 00:22:26.697
- KIMBERLY: Anybody see anything?
- We need some light.

273
00:22:26.697 --> 00:22:29.199
Activating power beam.

274
00:23:00.483 --> 00:23:03.611
- They gotta be around here somewhere.
- Activating power scope.

275
00:23:05.489 --> 00:23:07.991
TOMMY: Talk to me. Rocky. What do we got?

276
00:23:08.617 --> 00:23:13.623
I don't know what these purple creeps
are made of. but I can't lock 'em down.

277
00:23:13.623 --> 00:23:16.125
TOMMY: All right. Stay alert.

278
00:23:19.878 --> 00:23:23.007
- Over there!
- Let's power up!

279
00:23:23.007 --> 00:23:25.510
- ALL: Right!
- AISHA: Here they come!

280
00:23:29.890 --> 00:23:33.019
You guys make me sick. sick. sick!

281
00:23:53.041 --> 00:23:54.291
Back off!

282
00:23:56.795 --> 00:23:59.296
Have a nice flight!

283
00:24:02.426 --> 00:24:04.927
Later. dudes.

284
00:24:30.581 --> 00:24:33.083
It's gonna be one messy night.

285
00:24:40.592 --> 00:24:42.469
- Up and over?
- Let's do it!

286
00:24:51.854 --> 00:24:53.106
ADAM: Rocky. behind you!

287
00:24:54.356 --> 00:24:56.233
Goin' airborne!

288
00:24:59.987 --> 00:25:03.116
These guys don't know when to quit.
Double whammy?

289
00:25:03.116 --> 00:25:04.992
You're on.

290
00:25:06.244 --> 00:25:08.122
Uh-oh!

291
00:25:12.500 --> 00:25:14.378
Whoaaaa!

292
00:25:15.630 --> 00:25:17.507
That does it. Stegastinger!

293
00:25:23.138 --> 00:25:25.016
Did you miss me?

294
00:25:32.523 --> 00:25:35.024
Pterodactyl Thunderwhip!

295
00:25:35.024 --> 00:25:37.528
Have a nice trip! See you next fall.

296
00:25:41.909 --> 00:25:43.159
Bye-bye.

297
00:25:44.410 --> 00:25:46.287
Gotta love it.

298
00:26:08.811 --> 00:26:10.689
Hold on. Aisha!

299
00:26:13.191 --> 00:26:15.695
One. two. three. four. five. six!

300
00:26:16.320 --> 00:26:18.196
Aisha!

301
00:26:20.073 --> 00:26:21.951
- You OK?
- They're tough.

302
00:26:21.951 --> 00:26:25.080
- Let's finish these purple parasites.
- You said it.

303
00:26:38.219 --> 00:26:40.096
I want you guys to meet Saba.

304
00:26:52.609 --> 00:26:53.236
ALL: Uh-oh!

305
00:26:55.737 --> 00:26:56.989
ALL: Yeah!

306
00:26:58.866 --> 00:27:00.744
TOMMY: Now let's go find lvan.

307
00:27:03.413 --> 00:27:06.540
KIMBERLY: Hey. what's happening?

308
00:27:08.418 --> 00:27:10.921
BILLY: We're losing power.

309
00:27:17.176 --> 00:27:19.680
- What's goin' on?
- Alpha. come in.

310
00:27:23.433 --> 00:27:27.188
- Something's wrong.
- We'd better get back. Let's go. guys.

311
00:27:36.574 --> 00:27:39.076
BILLY: Oh. no.

312
00:27:39.076 --> 00:27:40.954
- Ooze.
- TOMMY: Let's get it open.

313
00:27:50.339 --> 00:27:52.841
TOMMY: Look at this place.

314
00:27:52.841 --> 00:27:55.343
TOMMY: I can't believe it.

315
00:27:55.970 --> 00:27:58.472
AISHA: What happened here?

316
00:27:59.724 --> 00:28:01.600
KIMBERLY: Oh. no.

317
00:28:05.979 --> 00:28:07.232
ADAM: Zordon!

318
00:28:07.232 --> 00:28:10.360
What's happening to him?

319
00:28:10.360 --> 00:28:12.863
Outside of his time warp. he's dying.

320
00:28:14.113 --> 00:28:15.991
BILLY: He needs power.

321
00:28:17.868 --> 00:28:20.372
Rangers.

322
00:28:20.372 --> 00:28:22.872
Thank goodness you are safe.

323
00:28:23.498 --> 00:28:26.002
Come on. we gotta get you back inside.

324
00:28:27.253 --> 00:28:29.756
I'm afraid that is impossible.

325
00:28:31.006 --> 00:28:34.135
The power has been destroyed.

326
00:28:35.387 --> 00:28:37.890
It is gone.

327
00:28:37.890 --> 00:28:39.766
The Zords...

328
00:28:39.766 --> 00:28:41.643
the weapons...

329
00:28:42.269 --> 00:28:44.147
all of it.

330
00:28:44.147 --> 00:28:48.527
The Power Rangers are no more.

331
00:28:48.527 --> 00:28:51.028
Ivan Ooze has won.

332
00:28:51.028 --> 00:28:54.783
- We're losing him.
- Zordon. you can't leave us!

333
00:28:56.035 --> 00:29:01.040
Ever since you came into our lives.
you've been like a father to us all.

334
00:29:01.666 --> 00:29:05.421
You must be strong.

335
00:29:10.425 --> 00:29:12.302
Rangers!

336
00:29:12.302 --> 00:29:14.179
TOMMY: Alpha.

337
00:29:16.682 --> 00:29:18.559
- Are you OK?
- I'll be fine.

338
00:29:19.184 --> 00:29:22.314
There may be a power
that can save Zordon.

339
00:29:22.314 --> 00:29:26.067
- What power?
- It is on the distant planet of Phaedos.

340
00:29:26.067 --> 00:29:30.445
It's very dangerous.
All who have tried for it have perished.

341
00:29:30.445 --> 00:29:35.452
- But we have to try. Alpha.
- Zordon's life force will not last long.

342
00:29:35.452 --> 00:29:38.581
- You won't have much time.
- How can we get it?

343
00:29:38.581 --> 00:29:42.960
Maybe if I can download the last plasmatic
morphing gem into the transport core.

344
00:29:42.960 --> 00:29:46.089
I might have just enough power
to get you there.

345
00:29:46.089 --> 00:29:50.469
- But there won't be any left to get you back.
- So. how do we get back?

346
00:29:50.469 --> 00:29:53.596
We have to hope that the power is there.

347
00:29:54.847 --> 00:29:56.724
Zordon's life depends on it.

348
00:29:58.601 --> 00:30:00.478
- Are you ready?
- Yeah.

349
00:30:04.859 --> 00:30:07.987
We may not have our powers.
but we're still the Power Rangers.

350
00:30:08.614 --> 00:30:11.741
Remember. Rangers.
Zordon doesn't have much time.

351
00:30:26.757 --> 00:30:30.511
Oh. no! Aye-yai-yai-yai-yai!

352
00:30:30.511 --> 00:30:33.015
Please hold on. Zordon!

353
00:30:39.271 --> 00:30:43.025
I can't believe it! How could he
let them slip through his hands?!

354
00:30:43.025 --> 00:30:46.154
He's no better than the rest of the hired help!

355
00:30:46.154 --> 00:30:48.656
Oh. give it a rest.

356
00:30:52.411 --> 00:30:56.165
- Hi. honey. I'm home!
- You egg-sucking purple pinhead!

357
00:30:56.165 --> 00:30:58.666
The Rangers are going after the great power!

358
00:30:59.293 --> 00:31:02.420
I thought you said this guy
was the master of disaster!

359
00:31:02.420 --> 00:31:04.924
He's nothing but
a slime-infested jelly doughnut!

360
00:31:06.174 --> 00:31:08.678
Finally someone shut her up.

361
00:31:10.555 --> 00:31:13.058
Your feebleness is staggering.

362
00:31:13.058 --> 00:31:16.187
You obviously need a vacation.

363
00:31:16.187 --> 00:31:21.190
I think circumstances
force us to choose a new leader...

364
00:31:21.190 --> 00:31:24.319
and I pick... me!

365
00:31:27.448 --> 00:31:30.575
Who does this clown think he's dealing with?

366
00:31:30.575 --> 00:31:33.705
The bogeyman is taking over.

367
00:31:34.330 --> 00:31:38.084
No one double-crosses Lord Zedd and lives!

368
00:31:39.961 --> 00:31:43.090
Oh. stop it! It tickles!

369
00:31:45.591 --> 00:31:47.468
My turn.

370
00:31:54.353 --> 00:31:59.984
- RITA: (squeaky voice) Way to go. bonehead!
- ZEDD: You can't trust anyone in this galaxy!

371
00:31:59.984 --> 00:32:03.737
- I love snow globes.
- RITA: Earthquake! Earthquake!

372
00:32:03.737 --> 00:32:06.866
Now you have a choice. You either serve me...

373
00:32:06.866 --> 00:32:09.993
or you can join these
insufferable dingledorks!

374
00:32:09.993 --> 00:32:13.747
- Goldar. get us out of here!
- Don't listen to that purple booger!

375
00:32:13.747 --> 00:32:15.624
ZEDD: Don't you dare betray me!

376
00:32:16.251 --> 00:32:20.631
- We never liked those dingledorks.
- PIG: You said it. They stink.

377
00:32:20.631 --> 00:32:26.261
So... what are we going to do about
the Power Rangers. oh my hideous one?

378
00:32:26.886 --> 00:32:28.763
Ah. yes.

379
00:32:28.763 --> 00:32:31.267
The Power Rangers.

380
00:32:31.267 --> 00:32:32.517
( snorts )

381
00:32:41.904 --> 00:32:43.781
- Good distance.
- Yeah.

382
00:33:11.935 --> 00:33:13.187
( squawking )

383
00:33:16.315 --> 00:33:23.198
Shut your beaks! Now.
my Tengu Warriors. you will fly to Phaedos.

384
00:33:23.198 --> 00:33:27.578
you will find the Power Rangers
and you will tear them apart!

385
00:33:32.583 --> 00:33:35.712
- GOLDAR: Go sic 'em. Tweety!
- PIG: Happy hunting!

386
00:34:11.376 --> 00:34:12.627
Wow.

387
00:34:17.006 --> 00:34:20.135
My gosh. Look at this place.

388
00:34:20.135 --> 00:34:23.888
AISHA: You guys! Over here! Quick!

389
00:34:34.525 --> 00:34:37.653
AISHA: Whoa. Looks like
somebody had a bad day.

390
00:34:37.653 --> 00:34:42.033
- What is it?
- I think the question is "What was it?"

391
00:34:42.659 --> 00:34:45.787
Definitely not the welcoming committee.
that's for sure.

392
00:34:45.787 --> 00:34:48.290
Come on. guys. we got a job to do.

393
00:35:18.949 --> 00:35:22.076
Taking over the world is one thing.

394
00:35:22.076 --> 00:35:25.205
Finding good help to run it for you.
that's the killer.

395
00:35:25.205 --> 00:35:28.333
Would you like me to make a few calls?

396
00:35:28.960 --> 00:35:33.965
No need. I'm going to recruit
the parents of Angel Grove.

397
00:35:33.965 --> 00:35:38.346
No offence. boss.
but they might find you a little disgusting.

398
00:35:38.346 --> 00:35:39.596
( belches )

399
00:35:39.596 --> 00:35:42.723
Well. I suppose you'd be the experts on that.

400
00:35:43.349 --> 00:35:48.354
- You forget. I'm a master of disguise.
- How could I forget? I never knew.

401
00:35:48.980 --> 00:35:51.484
First I'll turn them into zombies

402
00:35:51.484 --> 00:35:55.239
and then order them
to dig up my Ecto-Morphicons.

403
00:35:55.239 --> 00:35:57.116
How you gonna do that?

404
00:35:57.740 --> 00:36:03.372
By showing them the wonders
of being wicked with a little bit of lvan's ooze.

405
00:36:05.247 --> 00:36:07.125
( laughs )

406
00:36:10.879 --> 00:36:12.132
Ooh!

407
00:36:17.763 --> 00:36:23.395
Finally I get to finish
what I started 6.000 years ago!

408
00:36:23.395 --> 00:36:28.397
Little do they know my weapons of
destruction lie buried beneath their feet.

409
00:36:30.275 --> 00:36:32.152
( all laugh )

410
00:36:33.403 --> 00:36:37.783
- Stop it! Get to work!
- PIG: Yes. Your Royal Heinous Highness.

411
00:36:58.431 --> 00:37:00.308
Hey.

412
00:37:00.934 --> 00:37:01.809
You OK?

413
00:37:03.436 --> 00:37:05.939
I was just thinking about Zordon.

414
00:37:07.190 --> 00:37:10.944
You know. everything
we've been through together.

415
00:37:11.569 --> 00:37:14.074
Look. he's gonna make it.

416
00:37:15.324 --> 00:37:17.201
We'll find this power

417
00:37:17.827 --> 00:37:22.832
and then send that slimeball lvan Ooze
back to the sewer he crawled out of.

418
00:37:22.832 --> 00:37:24.709
Come on.

419
00:37:27.213 --> 00:37:29.090
What the heck was that?

420
00:37:30.968 --> 00:37:32.843
BILLY: Get down!

421
00:37:37.848 --> 00:37:39.099
TOMMY: Let's move!

422
00:37:42.229 --> 00:37:43.479
ROCKY: Look out!

423
00:37:49.111 --> 00:37:50.988
They're everywhere!

424
00:37:50.988 --> 00:37:52.864
Take cover!

425
00:38:00.372 --> 00:38:02.249
Back off.

426
00:38:12.886 --> 00:38:16.016
- Know the funny thing about morphin'?
- What?

427
00:38:16.016 --> 00:38:18.517
You don't appreciate it till you can't do it!

428
00:38:24.148 --> 00:38:26.650
TOMMY: Kimberly. behind you!

429
00:38:30.405 --> 00:38:32.909
Hang on. Kimberly!

430
00:38:35.411 --> 00:38:37.287
Somebody help me!

431
00:38:38.541 --> 00:38:41.041
- They're too strong!
- We need our powers!

432
00:38:45.421 --> 00:38:48.091
Let me go. Big Bird!

433
00:39:13.119 --> 00:39:14.996
( whistling noise )

434
00:39:18.123 --> 00:39:20.627
( whistling noise continues )

435
00:39:48.155 --> 00:39:50.659
That was amazing. Thanks.

436
00:39:52.537 --> 00:39:56.915
If you want to thank me.
go back to wherever it is you came from.

437
00:39:57.540 --> 00:40:00.045
- We can't.
- We were told there was a great power here.

438
00:40:00.045 --> 00:40:02.546
- Is it true?
- Yes.

439
00:40:02.546 --> 00:40:07.552
The ground is littered with the bones
of those who have tried for it and failed.

440
00:40:10.054 --> 00:40:13.183
Well. we're different. We won't fail.

441
00:40:17.562 --> 00:40:20.692
Leave Phaedos... before it's too late.

442
00:40:22.569 --> 00:40:25.696
Look. we don't want any trouble.
Our leader Zordon got hurt...

443
00:40:26.324 --> 00:40:27.574
Zordon?

444
00:40:28.200 --> 00:40:30.076
Did you say Zordon?

445
00:40:30.701 --> 00:40:33.205
You know Zordon? Who are you?

446
00:40:38.210 --> 00:40:42.591
I am Dulcea. master warrior
of the planet Phaedos.

447
00:40:43.841 --> 00:40:45.718
What has happened to Zordon?

448
00:40:45.718 --> 00:40:48.848
He was attacked by
this cosmic being named lvan Ooze.

449
00:40:48.848 --> 00:40:51.975
- lvan Ooze is free?
- You've heard of him?

450
00:40:52.601 --> 00:40:54.478
Ivan Ooze is a monster.

451
00:40:55.103 --> 00:40:58.232
If we don't hurry. your planet is doomed.

452
00:40:58.232 --> 00:41:00.110
Follow me.

453
00:41:20.131 --> 00:41:23.885
Alpha. I am deeply concerned
about the Rangers.

454
00:41:23.885 --> 00:41:26.388
Please. Zordon. save your strength.

455
00:41:26.388 --> 00:41:28.890
You need to rest.

456
00:41:28.890 --> 00:41:33.897
We must try to communicate with them.
It is possible I can help them.

457
00:41:33.897 --> 00:41:39.527
If I could locate a vertical deflector. we could
make contact through the viewing globe.

458
00:41:40.152 --> 00:41:43.281
Please... please hurry.

459
00:41:43.281 --> 00:41:45.783
Aye-yai-yai-yai-yai! Hold on.

460
00:41:47.035 --> 00:41:51.414
Guys and girls. girls and guys.
gather round and feast your eyes.

461
00:41:51.414 --> 00:41:53.918
I promise you all. you just can't lose.

462
00:41:54.543 --> 00:41:57.045
when you've got
your own supply of lvan's ooze.

463
00:41:57.045 --> 00:42:01.426
- BOY: What are we supposed to do with it?
- Show it to parents. show it to friends.

464
00:42:01.426 --> 00:42:04.553
When you've got your ooze.
the fun never ends.

465
00:42:04.553 --> 00:42:06.429
This is kinda gross.

466
00:42:06.429 --> 00:42:09.559
You may have heard
that looks can be deceiving.

467
00:42:09.559 --> 00:42:12.688
I'm sure that when you've tried it.
you all will be believing.

468
00:42:12.688 --> 00:42:15.191
And did I mention it's free?

469
00:42:15.191 --> 00:42:17.692
- I'll take some.
- Here you go. Who else?

470
00:42:20.195 --> 00:42:24.576
OK. there's enough for everybody.
Take it home in boxes. take it home in cases.

471
00:42:24.576 --> 00:42:28.954
If your parents try to stop you.
just throw it in their faces!

472
00:42:37.089 --> 00:42:39.592
BILLY: Dulcea. where are you taking us?

473
00:42:39.592 --> 00:42:42.720
You shall know soon enough.

474
00:42:42.720 --> 00:42:46.474
KIMBERLY: We have to hurry.
Zordon won't last much longer.

475
00:43:00.239 --> 00:43:01.491
TOMMY: Wow.

476
00:43:02.116 --> 00:43:04.618
- AISHA: Amazing.
- TOMMY: What is this place?

477
00:43:04.618 --> 00:43:08.999
DULCEA: These are the ancient ruins
of the Ninjetti Temple.

478
00:43:12.752 --> 00:43:16.507
There. beyond the Niola Jungle.
is the monolith.

479
00:43:17.132 --> 00:43:20.261
Inside awaits the power of the universe.

480
00:43:20.261 --> 00:43:24.015
The monolith
is heavily guarded against intruders.

481
00:43:24.015 --> 00:43:28.394
No one has ever survived
an attempt to reach it.

482
00:43:28.394 --> 00:43:30.895
Then how can we?

483
00:43:30.895 --> 00:43:33.400
You were chosen by Zordon.

484
00:43:34.025 --> 00:43:37.154
I have faith in his wisdom.

485
00:43:37.154 --> 00:43:39.657
Can you help us?

486
00:43:40.908 --> 00:43:45.288
We will call upon
the sacred animals of the Ninjetti for help.

487
00:44:04.642 --> 00:44:05.894
Fred!

488
00:44:46.561 --> 00:44:49.691
There. that should do it. Let's give it a whirl!

489
00:44:50.316 --> 00:44:54.696
Police have been fielding
hundreds of calls from concerned citizens

490
00:44:54.696 --> 00:44:57.823
as the number of missing parents
continues to grow.

491
00:44:58.450 --> 00:45:02.204
Hi. folks. Ivan Ooze here.
Are you bored with your work?

492
00:45:02.204 --> 00:45:07.209
Are you bored with your life? Then come on
down to Ooze City and let"s get sticky!

493
00:45:07.835 --> 00:45:09.713
Aye-yai-yai-yai-yai!

494
00:45:09.713 --> 00:45:12.215
Ivan's evil plot is taking shape.

495
00:45:15.343 --> 00:45:17.762
I just hope they're not too late.

496
00:45:40.203 --> 00:45:45.834
Buried deep within each of us
is an animal spirit waiting to be released.

497
00:45:47.085 --> 00:45:50.214
Close your eyes and look deep inside.

498
00:46:45.899 --> 00:46:50.905
Aisha. you are the bear.
fierce and unstoppable.

499
00:46:54.033 --> 00:46:58.413
Rocky. powerful. smart.
you are the mighty ape.

500
00:47:01.542 --> 00:47:06.546
Billy. you are the wolf. cunning and swift.

501
00:47:09.675 --> 00:47:15.306
Agile Kimberly. light as a feather.
you are the crane.

502
00:47:18.435 --> 00:47:19.312
Adam...

503
00:47:20.937 --> 00:47:24.066
- Adam. what's wrong?
- I'm a frog.

504
00:47:25.943 --> 00:47:30.322
Yes. a frog. Like the one you kiss...
to get a handsome prince.

505
00:47:34.701 --> 00:47:39.082
And you. Tommy. are the falcon.
winged lord of the skies.

506
00:47:42.210 --> 00:47:47.842
To be in harmony with a sacred animal
spirit is to have the force of the Ninjetti.

507
00:47:49.092 --> 00:47:53.472
To those who are Ninjetti.
anything is possible.

508
00:47:56.600 --> 00:48:00.355
But... I am afraid
you must do this on you own.

509
00:48:02.231 --> 00:48:04.735
You're not coming with us. Dulcea?

510
00:48:05.986 --> 00:48:07.863
If only I could.

511
00:48:07.863 --> 00:48:14.119
One step beyond this plateau and I would
begin to age as rapidly as Zordon is now.

512
00:48:15.371 --> 00:48:19.750
The strength is inside you. Trust it.

513
00:48:19.750 --> 00:48:22.253
Your sacred animals will be your guide.

514
00:48:26.008 --> 00:48:29.137
May your animal spirits watch over you.

515
00:48:44.778 --> 00:48:45.821
Dad?

516
00:48:49.784 --> 00:48:51.035
Dad?

517
00:48:53.539 --> 00:48:56.040
Dad? Where are you?

518
00:48:58.542 --> 00:49:01.672
IVAN: I forgot how slow parents are.

519
00:49:01.672 --> 00:49:05.426
I thought my Ecto-Morphicons
would be dug up by now.

520
00:49:07.928 --> 00:49:10.432
Oh. Goldie. I'm bored.

521
00:49:11.682 --> 00:49:13.559
Let's have some fun. Hey. you!

522
00:49:15.436 --> 00:49:17.313
Dance.

523
00:49:17.313 --> 00:49:19.189
( rock and roll music )

524
00:49:21.694 --> 00:49:23.570
Do the swim.

525
00:49:29.202 --> 00:49:31.704
- Ballet!
- (ballet music)

526
00:49:34.207 --> 00:49:36.710
( Ivan and Goldar laugh )

527
00:49:40.463 --> 00:49:41.089
Hey.

528
00:49:41.089 --> 00:49:44.218
Hey. boss! They're back!

529
00:49:46.720 --> 00:49:47.972
Ah!

530
00:49:48.597 --> 00:49:49.849
My Tengu.

531
00:49:57.357 --> 00:49:59.234
(squawking)

532
00:49:59.234 --> 00:50:02.361
Stop your screeching.

533
00:50:04.238 --> 00:50:07.993
- How did you fare?
- It couldn't have gone better.

534
00:50:07.993 --> 00:50:11.122
Threw one of 'em off a mountain.
one into a ragin' river.

535
00:50:11.746 --> 00:50:14.250
So. they've all been destroyed?

536
00:50:14.876 --> 00:50:17.377
- Well. we were about to destroy them. but...
- What?

537
00:50:18.005 --> 00:50:22.384
You didn't kill them? You call yourself Tengu
warriors? You're more like Tengu turkeys!

538
00:50:22.384 --> 00:50:25.512
I'll have you all stuffed and roasted!

539
00:50:25.512 --> 00:50:30.517
But. master. there was this monster with
these huge sticks and it kept twirling them...

540
00:50:30.517 --> 00:50:34.898
Sticks? Did these sticks
have a whistling sound?

541
00:50:35.524 --> 00:50:38.652
It was more like nails on a chalkboard.

542
00:50:38.652 --> 00:50:40.529
Dulcea.

543
00:50:40.529 --> 00:50:45.532
That miserable. manipulating.
loathsome she-devil of a witch!

544
00:50:45.532 --> 00:50:48.662
If she leads them to the great power.
everything will be ruined.

545
00:50:48.662 --> 00:50:53.668
- Do you want us to take another whack at it?
- How about takin' another quack at it?

546
00:50:57.422 --> 00:51:02.426
No time to waste. My Ecto-Morphicon
machines must be unearthed by sundown.

547
00:51:33.711 --> 00:51:36.212
It's time.

548
00:52:06.872 --> 00:52:10.627
BILLY: Man. this jungle goes on for ever.

549
00:52:10.627 --> 00:52:15.005
TOMMY: We've gotta keep movin'. guys.
Zordon's time is runnin' out.

550
00:52:37.696 --> 00:52:38.947
Dad!

551
00:52:41.451 --> 00:52:42.701
Dad!

552
00:52:43.328 --> 00:52:45.205
Hey. Dad!

553
00:52:45.830 --> 00:52:48.332
Dad. what's wrong with you?

554
00:52:48.332 --> 00:52:52.714
It's me - Fred.
Dad. we gotta get outta here!

555
00:52:52.714 --> 00:52:54.590
Hey. you!

556
00:52:56.467 --> 00:52:58.344
Get back to work!

557
00:52:58.344 --> 00:53:02.723
PIG: Yeah! Pick up those rocks!
Tote that barge! Lift that bale!

558
00:53:03.975 --> 00:53:06.477
GOLDAR: Put your weak backs into it!

559
00:53:06.477 --> 00:53:09.607
PIG: Yeah. I had a weak back
about a week back.

560
00:53:13.986 --> 00:53:20.868
Feast your eyes on the exoskeleton
of the Barbaric Hornitor!

561
00:53:20.868 --> 00:53:23.995
The Dreaded Scorpitron
should be close by.

562
00:53:23.995 --> 00:53:27.750
Once my lovely little Ecto-Morphicon
machines are up and running.

563
00:53:28.376 --> 00:53:31.504
spreading ooze throughout the world.

564
00:53:31.504 --> 00:53:36.511
I shall annihilate Angel Grove.
and then... the universe!

565
00:53:37.762 --> 00:53:42.141
PIG: # We're takin' over the world!
We're takin' over the world #

566
00:53:57.784 --> 00:54:02.163
- AISHA: What is this place?
- BILLY: Looks like some kind of graveyard.

567
00:54:05.917 --> 00:54:11.548
- KIMBERLY: I wonder what happened.
- ADAM: Personally. I'd rather not find out.

568
00:54:15.928 --> 00:54:19.056
- Welcome to Jurassic Park.
- AISHA: Very funny. Adam.

569
00:54:50.340 --> 00:54:52.217
TOMMY: Aisha. get outta there!

570
00:55:03.479 --> 00:55:05.357
Rocky!

571
00:55:11.613 --> 00:55:12.864
Uh-oh.

572
00:55:17.244 --> 00:55:19.121
Wait for me!

573
00:55:27.882 --> 00:55:29.758
- Tommy!
- Hang on!

574
00:55:31.009 --> 00:55:32.260
Tommy!

575
00:55:34.137 --> 00:55:36.640
All right. bonehead!

576
00:55:50.406 --> 00:55:52.907
- Tommy. hang on!
- Whoa! Whoa!

577
00:55:54.784 --> 00:55:56.662
Tommy!

578
00:55:58.539 --> 00:55:59.790
Whoa!

579
00:56:03.544 --> 00:56:06.047
Hold on tight. Tommy!

580
00:56:12.304 --> 00:56:16.057
Yo. fossil head!
I've got a bone to pick with you!

581
00:56:19.186 --> 00:56:21.063
Huh? Whoa!

582
00:56:24.817 --> 00:56:26.694
Are you OK?

583
00:56:26.694 --> 00:56:31.074
- Yeah. I'm fine.
- Biology finally paid off for you. huh?

584
00:56:31.074 --> 00:56:34.202
We should get outta here
before he pulls himself together.

585
00:56:34.828 --> 00:56:36.080
Yeah.

586
00:56:52.306 --> 00:56:58.561
GOLDAR: You there! Let's show a little
initiative! And you. get your rear in gear!

587
00:57:07.322 --> 00:57:10.450
Pick up the pace! We haven't got all day!

588
00:57:11.075 --> 00:57:15.455
- Hey. boss. construction is completed.
- PIG: Yeah. when's lunch?

589
00:57:15.455 --> 00:57:18.584
Parents of Angel Grove!

590
00:57:19.210 --> 00:57:22.337
You have completed my Ecto-Morphicons!

591
00:57:22.964 --> 00:57:27.968
But. frankly. I'm sick of your ugly faces
and your dull personalities.

592
00:57:27.968 --> 00:57:29.846
- Yeah!
- (giggles/snorts)

593
00:57:29.846 --> 00:57:33.600
You will return to the construction site
and leap to your doom.

594
00:57:33.600 --> 00:57:35.477
- Leap to your doom.
- Bye-bye.

595
00:57:36.103 --> 00:57:38.605
- GOLDAR: Bye-bye!
- GOLDAR: Aloha!

596
00:57:38.605 --> 00:57:40.483
GOLDAR: Arrivederci!

597
00:57:41.109 --> 00:57:42.985
- Dad!
- IVAN: Hasta la vista. baby.

598
00:57:42.985 --> 00:57:45.488
GOLDAR: See ya! Wouldn't wanna be ya!

599
00:57:45.488 --> 00:57:46.739
Ciao.

600
00:57:48.616 --> 00:57:51.119
See ya later. alligator.

601
00:57:51.119 --> 00:57:55.498
Finally. the moment of truth!

602
00:57:56.751 --> 00:57:59.879
Mordant. let the ooze flow!

603
00:57:59.879 --> 00:58:02.382
Comin' right up.

604
00:58:13.017 --> 00:58:17.397
Ooze. give my creatures life!

605
00:58:17.397 --> 00:58:21.777
Life. I tell you! Life!

606
00:58:39.296 --> 00:58:40.547
Excellent!

607
00:58:48.681 --> 00:58:51.183
Now my machines will destroy the city!

608
00:59:11.997 --> 00:59:13.249
ADAM: Wow.

609
00:59:13.249 --> 00:59:15.750
Hey. guys. check this out.

610
00:59:24.512 --> 00:59:26.388
BILLY: lncredible.

611
00:59:37.650 --> 00:59:40.152
Let's go. guys. Nice and easy.

612
01:00:13.939 --> 01:00:15.192
What do you think?

613
01:00:15.816 --> 01:00:17.692
Wait here.

614
01:00:39.592 --> 01:00:40.844
Tommy!

615
01:01:07.747 --> 01:01:09.625
- What now?
- Ninjetti!

616
01:01:09.625 --> 01:01:11.502
- Falcon!
- The frog!

617
01:01:11.502 --> 01:01:13.379
- The ape!
- The crane!

618
01:01:13.379 --> 01:01:15.883
- The wolf!
- Bear!

619
01:01:20.888 --> 01:01:22.764
These things are made of rock.

620
01:01:29.022 --> 01:01:30.899
These guys are strong.

621
01:01:49.669 --> 01:01:50.919
Yikes.

622
01:02:00.305 --> 01:02:02.182
Back off. boulder breath!

623
01:02:23.456 --> 01:02:25.333
Hang tight. Adam!

624
01:02:29.086 --> 01:02:30.337
Ever play leapfrog?

625
01:02:35.342 --> 01:02:37.219
- Adam!
- Hang on. Rocky!

626
01:02:42.226 --> 01:02:44.104
Hey. lava head!

627
01:02:49.735 --> 01:02:52.235
Thanks. Adam. Thought I was finished.

628
01:02:53.488 --> 01:02:55.365
That's one down. and three to go.

629
01:03:03.498 --> 01:03:04.750
Whoa!

630
01:03:06.628 --> 01:03:07.878
Somebody help!

631
01:03:12.259 --> 01:03:14.135
Let's talk about this.

632
01:03:14.760 --> 01:03:16.637
Guess not.

633
01:03:19.140 --> 01:03:21.643
Come on. roll!

634
01:03:21.643 --> 01:03:23.521
Hang on. Kimberly!

635
01:03:28.525 --> 01:03:31.654
They're strong. but they're not too smart.
Help me push.

636
01:03:31.654 --> 01:03:32.906
Right.

637
01:03:34.783 --> 01:03:36.659
KIMBERLY: Let's rock his world.

638
01:03:56.679 --> 01:03:59.184
What is this. pick-on-the-frog day?

639
01:04:02.938 --> 01:04:06.692
- Hey. Adam. could you use a hand?
- The thought crossed my mind.

640
01:04:07.317 --> 01:04:07.317
Adam!

641
01:04:11.697 --> 01:04:13.573
Elevator goin' up.

642
01:04:15.451 --> 01:04:17.328
BILLY: Elevator goin' down.

643
01:04:18.578 --> 01:04:20.456
Talk about a splitting headache.

644
01:04:24.835 --> 01:04:25.463
Whoa! That was close.

645
01:04:32.971 --> 01:04:34.848
- All right. Ready?
- Yeah.

646
01:04:35.472 --> 01:04:36.725
Go!

647
01:04:41.103 --> 01:04:43.606
Ninjetti corkscrew kick!

648
01:04:49.864 --> 01:04:51.114
Eightball. corner pocket!

649
01:05:03.002 --> 01:05:04.880
What now?

650
01:05:04.880 --> 01:05:08.007
- Whoa. What's happening?
- TOMMY: Look.

651
01:05:53.807 --> 01:05:56.310
The great power.

652
01:05:56.310 --> 01:05:58.813
The sacred animals.

653
01:06:28.846 --> 01:06:30.721
ROCKY: New Zords!

654
01:06:48.867 --> 01:06:50.744
- We did it!
- Our morphers are on line.

655
01:06:50.744 --> 01:06:52.620
- We got the power!
- Hang on. Zordon!

656
01:06:53.246 --> 01:06:55.123
- We're on our way.
- Let's do it.

657
01:07:07.637 --> 01:07:09.514
DULCEA: Good luck. Rangers.

658
01:07:23.905 --> 01:07:28.910
Citizens of Angel Grove.
how do you like my friends. huh?

659
01:07:55.189 --> 01:07:57.692
The boys are back in town!

660
01:07:57.692 --> 01:08:00.945
Long live the King of Ooze!

661
01:08:03.364 --> 01:08:05.867
The mayor has declared a state of emergency.

662
01:08:05.867 --> 01:08:09.621
He"s asked that the city
be immediately evacuated.

663
01:08:10.246 --> 01:08:12.123
Angel Grove has never before known...

664
01:08:12.123 --> 01:08:16.505
Aye-yai-yai-yai-yai! Ivan's evil machines
are destroying Angel Grove!

665
01:08:17.130 --> 01:08:19.007
Alpha...

666
01:08:19.632 --> 01:08:21.507
keep trying.

667
01:08:21.507 --> 01:08:24.012
TV: Where are the Power Rangers?

668
01:08:27.766 --> 01:08:31.520
I love the smell of destruction in the evening.

669
01:08:31.520 --> 01:08:33.398
Me. too.

670
01:08:33.398 --> 01:08:35.274
What's that smell?

671
01:08:35.900 --> 01:08:39.029
Inconceivable.

672
01:08:39.654 --> 01:08:42.156
The Power Rangers!

673
01:08:47.786 --> 01:08:51.541
- Oh. man! Look at this mess.
- This is lvan's handiwork.

674
01:08:51.541 --> 01:08:54.670
- Let's get back to the command centre.
- Wait. What was that?

675
01:08:54.670 --> 01:08:57.172
I think we're about to find out. Look!

676
01:09:02.803 --> 01:09:07.184
- Whoa. What is that thing?
- lvan's been busy while we were away.

677
01:09:10.937 --> 01:09:12.187
Whoa!

678
01:09:14.692 --> 01:09:17.819
- What's that?
- AISHA: There's another one.

679
01:09:17.819 --> 01:09:20.323
KIMBERLY: And it's even uglier.

680
01:09:22.200 --> 01:09:24.703
- Whoa.
- We've gotta stop these things.

681
01:09:24.703 --> 01:09:28.456
- We've got new Ninja Zords. Let's use 'em!
- Right!

682
01:09:28.456 --> 01:09:30.333
Ninja crane Zord!

683
01:09:30.333 --> 01:09:32.210
Ninja wolf Zord!

684
01:09:32.210 --> 01:09:33.461
Ninja frog Zord!

685
01:09:34.087 --> 01:09:34.712
Ninja ape Zord!

686
01:09:34.712 --> 01:09:37.842
Ninja bear Zord!

687
01:09:37.842 --> 01:09:39.718
Ninja falcon Zord!

688
01:09:42.221 --> 01:09:44.098
GOLDAR: Uh-oh!

689
01:09:52.232 --> 01:09:54.109
- Check it out!
- Ninja Zords!

690
01:09:54.735 --> 01:09:55.359
Cool!

691
01:09:55.359 --> 01:09:56.611
- Yes!
- Awesome!

692
01:10:03.495 --> 01:10:05.997
Oh. no! It's the Zords!

693
01:10:05.997 --> 01:10:09.752
Ah. Zords. schmords.
I'll crush 'em like roaches.

694
01:10:09.752 --> 01:10:12.879
- Let's do it!
- Right! Ninja Zords power up!

695
01:10:19.760 --> 01:10:21.638
Ready to ride. Yes!

696
01:10:21.638 --> 01:10:25.392
- All systems on line.
- Activating weapon systems.

697
01:10:25.392 --> 01:10:27.896
- Nice stereo.
- We're outta here!

698
01:10:42.285 --> 01:10:44.789
(parents chanting) Leap to our doom.

699
01:10:45.415 --> 01:10:47.291
Leap to our doom.

700
01:10:47.291 --> 01:10:50.420
Leap to our doom.

701
01:10:52.297 --> 01:10:54.799
# Uh-oh. we're in trouble #

702
01:10:55.424 --> 01:10:57.927
# Something's come along
and it's burst our bubble #

703
01:10:58.553 --> 01:10:59.805
# Yeah. yeah #

704
01:11:08.564 --> 01:11:10.440
Hey. everyone!

705
01:11:15.447 --> 01:11:20.452
Listen up! You all think
this is one big party. don't you?

706
01:11:21.077 --> 01:11:24.206
- Yeah!
- Well. you've all been brainwashed.

707
01:11:24.832 --> 01:11:29.211
Ivan's taking over the planet
and he's using all of us in his plans!

708
01:11:29.211 --> 01:11:32.340
- And he's got our parents.
- What are you talking about?

709
01:11:32.340 --> 01:11:34.842
Look. lvan Ooze is evil.

710
01:11:34.842 --> 01:11:40.473
And if you don't come with me right now. our
parents are gonna die! You gotta believe me!

711
01:11:43.602 --> 01:11:47.981
TOMMY: Rangers. I'm over the east quadrant.
My sensors are pickin' up a disturbance.

712
01:11:48.607 --> 01:11:50.485
I'm goin' in.

713
01:11:51.111 --> 01:11:54.239
Somebody call for an exterminator?
I've got a lock.

714
01:11:57.367 --> 01:11:59.245
Rockets away!

715
01:12:08.004 --> 01:12:09.881
I've been hit! I'm pullin' out!

716
01:12:09.881 --> 01:12:13.010
Don't worry. Tommy. Frog Zord is in position.

717
01:12:14.886 --> 01:12:16.763
We got 'em now. boss.

718
01:12:16.763 --> 01:12:20.518
Touch me again.
you'll be chicken wings in the morning.

719
01:12:24.897 --> 01:12:26.774
ADAM: Tongue-tied and twisted.

720
01:12:26.774 --> 01:12:28.650
Yee-hah!

721
01:12:31.155 --> 01:12:35.534
Bad move. sparky.
You play with fire. you're gonna get burned.

722
01:12:41.165 --> 01:12:43.668
- I need backup!
- BILLY: l"m on my way!

723
01:12:46.171 --> 01:12:49.298
Wolf Zord approaching target.
Keep him tied up. I'm loading hydraulics.

724
01:12:49.925 --> 01:12:52.427
ADAM: I'm losin' him!

725
01:12:52.427 --> 01:12:54.304
Here goes!

726
01:12:55.556 --> 01:12:58.058
All right! Got him.

727
01:13:04.942 --> 01:13:07.442
Time to boogie with the bear.

728
01:13:11.197 --> 01:13:12.449
Whoa!

729
01:13:13.073 --> 01:13:14.951
I've been hit hard!

730
01:13:16.828 --> 01:13:19.330
Ape Zord locked on target.

731
01:13:20.583 --> 01:13:23.085
Yee-hah!

732
01:13:23.712 --> 01:13:25.589
Ride 'em. cowboy!

733
01:13:29.966 --> 01:13:33.096
- Hang in there. Rocky!
- I'm hangin'! I'm hangin'!

734
01:13:34.347 --> 01:13:37.476
FRED: Come on! We'll take the monorail!

735
01:13:41.229 --> 01:13:43.732
Let's get down to the construction site!

736
01:13:56.245 --> 01:14:00.000
All right. guys.
I've got a lock on the ooze man.

737
01:14:01.252 --> 01:14:01.877
Ah!

738
01:14:02.502 --> 01:14:05.007
Here comes that cute
little Pink Ranger to the rescue.

739
01:14:05.631 --> 01:14:08.760
Oh. you think she's cute too. huh?

740
01:14:09.385 --> 01:14:10.638
(lvan growls)

741
01:14:10.638 --> 01:14:15.015
- One order of toasted slime comin' up.
- So. you wanna play. huh?

742
01:14:20.022 --> 01:14:23.776
Ivan's got me in an electromagnetic deadlock!
I can't break free!

743
01:14:23.776 --> 01:14:26.278
TOMMY: Hang on. Kimberly!

744
01:14:27.531 --> 01:14:30.658
I'm getting airsick up here!

745
01:14:30.658 --> 01:14:34.411
My stabilisers have ruptured!
I can't hold on much longer!

746
01:14:36.288 --> 01:14:40.043
- I'm burning up in here!
- AISHA: Kimberly. use your thrusters!

747
01:14:40.669 --> 01:14:42.546
Right! Now. which button?

748
01:14:44.424 --> 01:14:45.674
Aaaaaggghhh!

749
01:14:46.925 --> 01:14:49.428
- I'll deal with you later.
- Yeah. later.

750
01:14:58.187 --> 01:14:59.439
Ah. Oozed.

751
01:15:02.567 --> 01:15:05.695
I'm losing my grip!
I can't hold on much longer!

752
01:15:08.825 --> 01:15:12.580
Falcon Zord is back in the game.
Adam. disengage. I've got a clear shot!

753
01:15:12.580 --> 01:15:14.456
He's all yours.

754
01:15:15.081 --> 01:15:18.210
All right. big guy. it's lights out for you.

755
01:15:19.460 --> 01:15:21.964
Rockets away!

756
01:15:30.723 --> 01:15:34.476
- He's outta there!
- Target neutralised. Let's get the other one.

757
01:15:36.981 --> 01:15:38.858
He's too strong! I can't take him down!

758
01:15:48.867 --> 01:15:51.369
Everybody close in. This street's a dead end.

759
01:15:53.247 --> 01:15:55.751
IVAN: They've destroyed
my beautiful creation.

760
01:15:55.751 --> 01:16:03.883
Now I'm beginning to get really angry!

761
01:16:17.023 --> 01:16:19.525
Oh. I'm gonna be sick.

762
01:16:19.525 --> 01:16:21.403
IVAN: I feel big again!

763
01:16:22.029 --> 01:16:24.530
Go get 'em. booger man!

764
01:16:28.284 --> 01:16:31.414
Whoa. Somebody call a plastic surgeon.

765
01:16:33.916 --> 01:16:36.418
Oh. no!

766
01:16:36.418 --> 01:16:38.296
I'm outta here!

767
01:16:42.677 --> 01:16:45.178
Time for a little swordplay.

768
01:16:50.184 --> 01:16:53.687
- He destroyed the monorail track.
- We need Ninja Megazord power now!

769
01:16:54.314 --> 01:16:56.815
Ninja Megazord. power up!

770
01:17:08.078 --> 01:17:11.207
Monorail's in trouble.
I'll complete docking sequence later.

771
01:17:11.207 --> 01:17:13.708
KIMBERLY: We"ll take care of lvan.

772
01:17:18.089 --> 01:17:20.593
# Go. go. Power Rangers #

773
01:17:20.593 --> 01:17:23.720
# Mighty Morphin Power Rangers #

774
01:17:23.720 --> 01:17:25.597
Crane Zord locked on.

775
01:17:26.224 --> 01:17:27.474
Checking out.

776
01:17:27.474 --> 01:17:29.978
Ninja battle mode now!

777
01:17:34.356 --> 01:17:37.486
- Activating Ninja Megazord battle mode.
- Power Sword. now!

778
01:17:41.239 --> 01:17:43.117
Shall we tango?

779
01:17:49.373 --> 01:17:51.876
- Oh. no.
- What is that?

780
01:17:51.876 --> 01:17:54.379
- The track's broken!
- Oh. no!

781
01:17:57.506 --> 01:17:59.383
Hang on. kids.

782
01:18:05.642 --> 01:18:09.395
- Falcon Zord is comin' in for a landin'.
- Everybody hang on!

783
01:18:15.025 --> 01:18:15.650
All right! Yeah! Whoo!

784
01:18:16.276 --> 01:18:19.405
Good luck. kids.

785
01:18:25.662 --> 01:18:27.538
Power Sword has been destroyed.

786
01:18:30.667 --> 01:18:33.797
- Pressure's dropping!
- Negative control!

787
01:18:33.797 --> 01:18:38.174
- Tommy. we need your help!
- Hang tight. guys. I'm on my way.

788
01:18:41.304 --> 01:18:45.059
- Everybody hang on!
- IVAN: Next stop. Angel Grove First National.

789
01:18:45.059 --> 01:18:46.309
Whoaaa!

790
01:18:46.309 --> 01:18:48.186
ADAM: Brace for impact!

791
01:18:55.694 --> 01:18:57.572
- All systems down!
- He's closing in!

792
01:18:58.197 --> 01:19:01.952
- Tommy. get your butt down here!
- Comin' in to complete the sequence.

793
01:19:07.583 --> 01:19:08.833
Ninja Falcon Megazord!

794
01:19:11.962 --> 01:19:15.091
Let's get Ooze outta here
before he destroys everything.

795
01:19:15.091 --> 01:19:17.594
- I'll set a course for outer space.
- Good idea.

796
01:19:17.594 --> 01:19:18.846
Let's do it!

797
01:19:26.979 --> 01:19:30.108
You can run. but you can't hide.

798
01:19:31.358 --> 01:19:33.235
Yee-hah!

799
01:19:43.079 --> 01:19:44.330
(chanting) Leap to our doom.

800
01:19:46.208 --> 01:19:48.710
Leap to our doom.

801
01:19:49.961 --> 01:19:51.839
Leap to our doom.

802
01:19:53.089 --> 01:19:54.966
Leap to our doom.

803
01:20:01.224 --> 01:20:03.102
It's our parents!

804
01:20:14.989 --> 01:20:19.367
You guys try and stop them.
And you two come with me.

805
01:20:34.383 --> 01:20:37.513
- Guys. I think I know a way to get rid of lvan.
- Really? How?

806
01:20:37.513 --> 01:20:40.015
- Ryan's Comet.
- Billy. that's brilliant!

807
01:20:40.015 --> 01:20:42.519
- What?
- We get lvan in the comet's path...

808
01:20:42.519 --> 01:20:45.022
And kaboom! He's space dust.

809
01:20:45.022 --> 01:20:47.523
- All right. guys. main thrusters.
- Right!

810
01:20:56.908 --> 01:21:00.662
- We can't hold 'em back!
- We have to keep on trying!

811
01:21:19.433 --> 01:21:21.936
Turn it on!

812
01:21:45.086 --> 01:21:48.214
Well. if it isn't that
double-dealing dough head!

813
01:21:48.840 --> 01:21:52.595
I hope those Rangers
put that lousy lowlife out of my misery!

814
01:21:52.595 --> 01:21:56.348
- Go. Rangers! Go. Rangers!
- Go. Rangers! Go. Rangers!

815
01:21:56.974 --> 01:22:00.102
We're approaching the comet's coordinates.

816
01:22:00.727 --> 01:22:03.856
All right. guys. this is it.
We'll wait here and lure him in.

817
01:22:03.856 --> 01:22:06.985
I'm gonna rip you apart Zord by Zord.

818
01:22:08.236 --> 01:22:10.739
TOMMY: Here he comes. Brace yourselves!

819
01:22:11.992 --> 01:22:13.869
(lvan laughs)

820
01:22:19.499 --> 01:22:22.000
- Micropressure's in the red!
- We're imploding!

821
01:22:22.000 --> 01:22:25.130
Bearing 009. We're in the comet's trajectory.

822
01:22:25.130 --> 01:22:26.381
We need to break free.

823
01:22:26.381 --> 01:22:29.509
IVAN: Have you hugged your Zords today?

824
01:22:32.638 --> 01:22:35.766
- Here it comes!
- We have to break his grip!

825
01:22:36.393 --> 01:22:38.893
Desperate times
call for desperate measures.

826
01:22:38.893 --> 01:22:42.648
- What are you doing?
- Taking care of business.

827
01:22:47.028 --> 01:22:49.531
- We're outta here.
- Right!

828
01:22:54.536 --> 01:22:56.413
Oh. no.

829
01:23:20.815 --> 01:23:22.066
Yeah.

830
01:23:22.691 --> 01:23:24.568
- Skull!
- Bulk...

831
01:23:31.451 --> 01:23:32.703
Dad!

832
01:23:33.954 --> 01:23:35.830
- Fred!
- Dad!

833
01:23:45.842 --> 01:23:47.720
I love you. son.

834
01:23:56.729 --> 01:23:57.979
Alpha!

835
01:23:57.979 --> 01:24:01.108
Rangers. you made it!

836
01:24:01.108 --> 01:24:04.862
But... I'm afraid you're too late.

837
01:24:05.487 --> 01:24:07.364
BILLY: Too late?

838
01:24:11.745 --> 01:24:13.622
This can't be happening.

839
01:24:41.152 --> 01:24:43.655
Remember what we learnt?

840
01:24:44.907 --> 01:24:49.286
To those who possess the great power.
all things are possible.

841
01:24:55.541 --> 01:24:58.045
Come on.

842
01:26:13.126 --> 01:26:14.376
Zordon!

843
01:26:14.376 --> 01:26:16.254
Rangers!

844
01:26:16.254 --> 01:26:19.382
He's alive! He's alive! He's alive!

845
01:26:19.382 --> 01:26:23.761
- We thought that you had...
- It is good to see you again. too.

846
01:26:32.189 --> 01:26:33.440
( # The Power" by Snap )

847
01:26:34.066 --> 01:26:35.944
- SKULL: We were awesome.
- BULK: lncredible!

848
01:26:36.568 --> 01:26:39.071
Ivan and his 50-foot monsters
had us surrounded.

849
01:26:39.697 --> 01:26:42.824
- There was no escape.
- We knew we were facing death in the eye.

850
01:26:42.824 --> 01:26:46.578
- We could smell death's breath.
- And death could use a mint.

851
01:26:46.578 --> 01:26:48.456
Can you believe those guys?

852
01:26:49.082 --> 01:26:51.584
I'm so hungry.

853
01:26:52.209 --> 01:26:54.087
- Hey. guys.
- Hey. Fred!

854
01:26:54.714 --> 01:26:58.468
- Hey! Rumour has it you're quite the hero.
- That's my man!

855
01:26:58.468 --> 01:27:02.221
I helped a bit.
The Power Rangers did most of the work.

856
01:27:02.221 --> 01:27:07.226
Hey. things got tough. you didn't panic.
You. my friend. demonstrated true bravery.

857
01:27:07.226 --> 01:27:11.607
It's like what you taught me about martial
arts: use your head. and above all. stay calm.

858
01:27:11.607 --> 01:27:15.361
I heard you're in line to be
a Ranger yourself one of these days.

859
01:27:15.361 --> 01:27:20.365
- Nah. that's impossible.
- Hey. anything's possible.

860
01:27:20.365 --> 01:27:23.494
- You really think so?
- I know so.

861
01:27:25.370 --> 01:27:30.376
- Fred Kelman. the Silver Ranger.
- It does have a certain ring to it.

862
01:27:32.254 --> 01:27:34.756
Fred Kelman the Gold Ranger.

863
01:27:39.136 --> 01:27:40.387
Check it out!

864
01:27:41.639 --> 01:27:44.767
# We'll get higher and higher #

865
01:27:44.767 --> 01:27:46.643
# Straight up we'll climb #

866
01:27:47.894 --> 01:27:51.024
# We'll get higher and higher #

867
01:27:51.649 --> 01:27:54.151
# Leave it all behind #

868
01:27:56.655 --> 01:27:59.782
# So. baby. dry your eyes #

869
01:28:00.410 --> 01:28:02.911
- All right!
- I don't believe it.

870
01:28:07.291 --> 01:28:09.794
- Power Rangers?
- Bulk and Skull!

871
01:28:10.418 --> 01:28:13.548
# Cos we belong #

872
01:28:13.548 --> 01:28:16.675
# In a world that must be strong #

873
01:28:17.303 --> 01:28:22.433
# Oh. that's what dreams are made of #

874
01:28:23.684 --> 01:28:30.565
# Oh. that's what dreams are made of #

875
01:29:11.862 --> 01:29:14.363
I am King Goldar.

876
01:29:14.989 --> 01:29:17.492
the ruler of the universe!

877
01:29:25.000 --> 01:29:26.251
Uh-oh.

